Just to inform you, Cyberwolf, Ramulus has been in the Neo Beast Wars since 
almost the very begining. I know Lunarpine has no way of knowing that, but 
I'm just saying.

::Ramulus::

Ramulus looks over at Lunarpine, hoping the fellow Maximal would catch 
Ramhorn. He growls as he looks at the retreating Newcomers, then back at 
Lunarpine.

"Is he alive?" he asks, reffering to Ramhorn.
